commit.message:
* lang-specs.h: Pass -I* options to f771.

From-SVN: r35832

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@
+2000-08-21  Jakub Jelinek  <jakub@redhat.com>
+
+	* lang-specs.h: Pass -I* options to f771.
